</p>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Spinning:</strong> 6'6" ultralight or light-action rods
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Fly Fishing:</strong> 4- to 5-weight rods with floating lines
    </li>
</ul>
<p>
